### POST /api/v1/payments/simulate-webhook
### Descripción: Simular webhook (solo entorno Development). AllowAnonymous.
### Headers requeridos: ninguno (auth no requerida).
### Códigos: 200 OK | 404 (no Development o payment not found) | 400 PAYMENT_NOT_SIMULATABLE

# @name simulateWebhook
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/payments/simulate-webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "{{PAYMENT_ID}}",
  "eventType": "payment_intent.succeeded"
}

### Response esperado (200): (sin body)
### Response error (404): Solo en Development; Payment not found
### Response error (400): Payment has no ExternalPaymentId
